title: Elvish I-Z
author: jkru2133
pages:
#- I

Iasatar - Thank you

Imai - Red

Imith - Blood

Iriv'teshai - War-companion

I Satanas - I Know
#- J

Ja nevnay - An oath, roughly translating to 'velvet sky'
#- K

Kaleanae - Observer, Watcher

Katamah! - reach for the stars

Katar Neenar - No idea, don't know at all

Keh? - What?
#- Keroth - brother

K'eth - Breath of the Goddess

Kholai - White/Bright

Kieran - Beloved sister

Kin'ai - Violet/purple
#- K'th! - Obey

Kusanar - Twilight

Kyela - Love
#- L
Luin - blue

Leire'sinn - Clear Sight
#- M
Mellon - Friend

Minas - Tower

Mithrin - Grey

Malanai - Mother

Mana - No

Marara - Child
#- Milana - Forest

Mileana Tar - You are thanked

Myhidr - Lover/Companion
#- N
Namáriëor Navaer - Farewell

Nan - Vale

Ndengina - Kill

Nikerym - Captain

Numen - West

Namarie - Well Met
#- Narwa - Remember

Nehatah - Brain Lock

Ninaste - Leader of the Hunt

Nish'allien terestai - Go back to the trees

Nish - far from

Nis'tai - Dishonorable
#- O

Oforfamar - Leadership
#- P
Parma - Book

Pelargir - Garth of Royal Ships

Peredhil - half-elvish or half elf

Palantíri - Far seeing

Pira - little
#- Q
Quendi - the Speakers

Quel re- Good day
